abstract: A bomb exploded Tuesday outside the Athens office of JPMorgan Chase, but the police and the company said it caused no injuries and only minor damage.
snippet: A bomb exploded Tuesday outside the Athens office of JPMorgan Chase, but the police and the company said it caused no injuries and only minor damage.
lead_paragraph: A bomb exploded Tuesday outside the Athens office of JPMorgan Chase, but the police and the company told Reuters that it caused no injuries and only minor damage.

headline.main: Bomb Explodes at Athens Office of JPMorgan
